data.description: Here it is, your chance to live the dream lifestyle in sunny Dunedin, Florida! Steps to the library, the main street attractions, the Pinellas Trail, and the pier! This location is close to world famous Clearwater Beach, as well as Honeymoon, Island and the Dunedin Causeway. This four bedroom home is situated on an extra large quarter acre corner lot, which affords the possibility to expand to an even larger house in the future! The solid fourth bedroom conversion offers plenty of extra space. Just a few short blocks from world, famous TD ballpark. “TD Ballpark, originally Dunedin Stadium at Grant Field, is a baseball field located in Dunedin, Florida. The stadium was built in 1990 and holds 8,500 fans. It is the spring training home of the Toronto Blue Jays, as well as home to the Dunedin Blue Jays of the Florida State League and the Dunedin High School Falcons baseball team.” Get into Dunedin on the ground floor. Updates include kitchen, fourth bedroom and bathroom. Come see it and start your living your Florida lifestyle!
